test_list_of_zeros:
assert [57, 23, 23] == [0]
  At index 0 diff: 57 != 0
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 23
  Full diff:
  - [0]
  + [57, 23, 23]
test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [57, 23, 23] == [57]
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 23
  Full diff:
  - [57]
  + [57, 23, 23]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [57, 23, 23] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 57
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [57, 23, 23]
